GUESS A FOUR DIGIT NUMBER BYENTERING   FOUR DIGITS.  IF A BLANKIS GIVEN IN    RESPONSE; NONE OF THEDIGITS YOU        ENTERED ARE IN THESOLUTION.EACH '1' INDICATES THAT A DIGIT ISIN   THE SOLUTION AND IN THE SAMEPOSITION.  EACH '2' INDICATES THAT ADIGIT IS IN   THE SOLUTION BUT NOTIN THE SAME        POSITION.